  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">Qwen3的技术报告：&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3/blob/main/Qwen3_Technical_Report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3/blob/main/Qwen3_Technical_Report.pdf</a></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们用大模型翻译了这份技术报告并提供英中对照版，感兴趣的朋友可以关注AINLP公众号回复'qwen3'获取这份技术报告的英中对照版：</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AINLP\" data-alias=\"nlpjob\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/nW2ZPfuYqSKAnqcViaIWJ40GKChb8uoLoichr44nhO2OSPBzMxhdosvv3Ljc695woogSyoIMlsiaIRuk8ur4jpHZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"一个有趣有AI的自然语言处理公众号：关注AI、NLP、大模型LLM、机器学习、推荐系统、计算广告等相关技术。公众号可直接对话双语聊天机器人，尝试对对联、作诗机、藏头诗生成器、自动写作等，查询相似词，测试NLP相关工具包。\" data-id=\"MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"0\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.413888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001034\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0629dbed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZvlMsfNDDjmyISicxqfjhYh2I7JZcYluNes3kF9GT3ccsbqyIw1R3M9S55VGCfNovLDWeiadeSMlHjbe8ztBibnxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.413888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001035\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=13930603&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZvlMsfNDDjmyISicxqfjhYh2I7JZcYluNq3h5n6A4BCHNwE4qpyAq3uictSLw3OvicmUGn7HnUMicbPfswpvRMn7kA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.413888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001036\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09017b3d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZvlMsfNDDjmyISicxqfjhYh2I7JZcYluNB0rh9We3NBC6ZuZlKFDW4dZJlRAbMW4DjYraZSMavfOjHgTKCbsKqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.413888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001038\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30e711bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZvlMsfNDDjmyISicxqfjhYh2I7JZcYluNrIPTKDSycHkgkcr3rt2Dhd54keFAf9dBqJGVzAKVZIbRQUC5DiabjNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.413888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001037\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=886da602&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZvlMsfNDDjmyISicxqfjhYh2I7JZcYluN0mic154qib6XKdQ3ibycZbzT4ibKFibIacMFFIXmaF3zZSO6EuY8HM9TkJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.413888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100001039\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a821f949&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZvlMsfNDDjmyISicxqfjhYh2I7JZcYluNfdyre0mNzUxRmfbgDgL5ePgib4X0TBff0A3qqt02MAwDuR0FINnqHbg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对照版全文70页，以下是这份技术报告的简单解读：</span></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一、引言</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 是 Qwen 模型家族的最新版本，它在性能、效率和多语言能力方面都取得了显著进步。该模型系列包含从 0.6B 到 235B 参数规模不等的多种模型，包括密集型和专家混合型（MoE）架构，旨在满足不同下游应用的需求。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">二、模型创新点</span></span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">思考模式与非思考模式的融合</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 首次将思考模式（用于复杂多步推理）和非思考模式（用于快速上下文驱动响应）集成到一个统一框架中，消除了在不同模型之间切换的需要。这种设计使用户能够根据查询或聊天模板动态切换模式，提高了模型的灵活性和实用性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">思考预算机制</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 引入了思考预算机制，允许用户在推理过程中自适应地分配计算资源，从而根据任务复杂性在延迟和性能之间取得平衡。这一创新使用户能够更精细地控制模型在任务执行过程中的推理努力程度。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">高效的多语言支持</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 的预训练涵盖了 119 种语言和方言，相比前代 Qwen2.5，多语言支持范围从 29 种扩展到 119 种，显著增强了跨语言理解和生成能力，提高了模型在全球范围内的可用性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">三、模型架构</span></span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">密集型模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 的密集型模型架构与 Qwen2.5 相似，采用了分组查询注意力（GQA）、SwiGLU、旋转位置嵌入（RoPE）和 RMSNorm（预归一化）等技术。与 Qwen2.5 相比，Qwen3 移除了 QKV 偏置，并引入了 QK-Norm 以确保训练的稳定性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">专家混合型（MoE）模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 的 MoE 模型在基本架构上与密集型模型相同，但具有更精细的专家分割。Qwen3 MoE 模型共有 128 个专家，每个令牌激活 8 个专家，且不再使用共享专家。此外，Qwen3 MoE 采用了全局批次负载均衡损失，以鼓励专家专业化。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">四、预训练</span></span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">预训练数据</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 的预训练数据集包含约 36 万亿个令牌，涵盖 119 种语言和方言，包括编码、STEM、推理任务、书籍、多语言文本和合成数据。通过使用 Qwen2.5-VL 模型提取大量 PDF 文档中的文本，并利用 Qwen2.5 等模型生成不同格式的合成数据，进一步扩展了预训练数据的规模和多样性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">预训练阶段</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 的预训练分为三个阶段。第一阶段（S1）在约 30 万亿个令牌上进行训练，主要侧重于语言熟练度和通用世界知识；第二阶段（S2）通过增加 STEM、编码、推理和合成数据的比例来优化预训练语料库，进一步提高模型的推理能力；第三阶段（S3）收集高质量的长上下文语料库，将上下文长度扩展至 32,768 个令牌。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">五、后训练</span></span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">长链推理冷启动（Long-CoT Cold Start）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：通过精心构建的数据集，涵盖数学、编码、逻辑推理和通用 STEM 问题等多个类别，为模型奠定基础推理模式。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">推理强化学习（Reasoning RL）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：利用 GRPO 算法更新模型参数，注重提高模型的推理能力。该阶段收集了 3,995 个查询 - 验证器对，用于模型训练。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">思考模式融合（Thinking Mode Fusion）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：将非思考能力集成到已具备思考能力的模型中，通过持续的监督微调（SFT）和设计聊天模板来融合两种模式。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通用强化学习（General RL）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：旨在全面增强模型在各种场景下的能力和稳定性，构建了涵盖 20 多个不同任务的复杂奖励系统，这些任务针对指令遵循、格式遵循、偏好对齐、代理能力和特定场景能力等方面进行优化。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">六、模型性能评估</span></span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:decimal;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">预训练模型评估</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 系列的预训练基础模型在多个基准测试中表现出色，包括通用任务、数学和 STEM 任务、编码任务以及多语言任务。与 Qwen2.5 和其他领先的开源基础模型相比，Qwen3 在大多数任务中取得了更高的性能，即使在参数规模较小的情况下也能与更大规模的模型相媲美。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">后训练模型评估</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;：Qwen3 的后训练模型在思考模式和非思考模式下均展现出竞争力。旗舰模型 Qwen3-235B-A22B 在多个基准测试中取得了优异的成绩，与其他推理模型和非推理模型相比，展现出强大的推理能力和全面的通用能力。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">七、结论与未来研究方向</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3 作为 Qwen 系列的最新版本，凭借其创新的思考模式和非思考模式融合、思考预算机制以及高效的多语言支持，在多个领域的任务中取得了卓越的性能。未来，Qwen3 的研究将集中在扩大预训练规模、改进模型架构和训练方法、以及增加强化学习的计算资源等方面，以进一步提升模型的能力和应用范围。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以上报告详细阐述了 Qwen3 的技术特点、创新点、架构设计、训练方法以及性能评估等方面的内容，展示了 Qwen3 在大型语言模型领域的先进性和竞争力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">感兴趣的朋友可以关注AGI公众号回复'qwen3'获取这份英中对照版</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文是对 Qwen3 技术报告的简要解读，概述了其在模型架构、训练方法、功能创新及性能评估方面的核心亮点，强调了其思考模式融合、思考预算机制及多语言支持的进步。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文是对 Qwen3 技术报告的简要解读，概述了其在模型架构、训练方法、功能创新及性能评估方面的核心亮点，强调了其思考模式融合、思考预算机制及多语言支持的进步。",
  "summary": "本文是对 Qwen3 技术报告的摘要和解读，旨在向读者介绍 Qwen3 系列大型语言模型的关键技术创新与进展。文章详细阐述了 Qwen3 在模型设计上的独特性，包括其首次融合的思考模式与非思考模式、创新的思考预算机制以及扩展至 119 种语言的高效多语言支持。在模型架构方面，Qwen3 涵盖了密集型和 MoE（专家混合型）两种，并对架构细节（如 GQA、SwiGLU、RoPE、RMSNorm 等）进行了更新。预训练阶段，模型在 36 万亿令牌上分三阶段进行，特别注重长上下文语料和合成数据的使用。后训练则引入了长链推理冷启动、推理强化学习等复杂机制。最终，文章通过多维度的性能评估，展示了 Qwen3 在通用任务、数学、编码及多语言能力上超越前代和竞品的表现，并展望了未来的研究方向。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Qwen3 创新性地融合了思考模式与非思考模式，提高了模型的灵活性和实用性。",
      "explanation": "通过动态切换推理模式，模型能根据任务复杂度自适应调整，避免了不同模型之间的切换开销，提升了用户体验。"
    },
